{"tid":2238121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2019冬季流感 錄得625宗嚴重個案　357人死亡","createTime":"2020-10-11T01:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T01:27:50.000Z","uid":155431,"like":20,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"efd8d7dbbf557e7f57a354677dba7f54c42b664a","tid":2238121,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T01:06:37.000Z","msg":"成人方面，本流感季節期間（二○一八年十二月三十日開始一周至截至四月六日一周止），共錄得601宗與流感相關而需入住深切治療部或死亡的個案，包括356人死亡。至於兒童（十八歲以下）嚴重個案，同期共錄得24宗（一人死亡）。約73%沒有曾接種今季季節性流感疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n另外，院舍和學校流感樣疾病爆發個案數目從截至一月十九日一星期的209宗（涉及1 575人），下降至截至四月六日一星期的12宗（69人）。本星期截至昨日（四月九日）錄得九宗流感樣疾病爆發個案，涉及34人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好驚 原來當年流感好多人死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解當年啲人唔戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370001839d88648d67936e076807143559a15c3e","tid":2238121,"uid":62020,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解唔停工停市"},{"pid":"e642c7f3cae3ed5c6b3215f92a44bd7c2bee0452","tid":2238121,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T01:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5437d6f788ea2bae92eaa3125967d5b0310233","tid":2238121,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T01:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d83e6050dac888c4c27f3d25642f383109f31d2","tid":2238121,"uid":358542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T01:46:19.000Z","msg":"你知道得太多了"},{"pid":"b30ea87651df93a39ee6d0a03f045c0a4180533f","tid":2238121,"uid":57848,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T01:59:15.000Z","msg":"果陣乜防疫措施都冇都係死3百幾<br />\n<br />\n依家出街帶口罩，限聚限飛，你望下依家死咗幾多人，不如你改咗個名佢啦，好柒啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a739f3e41